---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { generateBreadcrumbSchema } from '../utils/seo';

const title = 'DMCA Policy | FixMissingDLL';
const description = 'DMCA Policy and copyright information for FixMissingDLL.com. Learn how to submit a takedown notice for copyrighted content.';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: 'https://fixmissingdll.com/' },
  { name: 'DMCA Policy', url: 'https://fixmissingdll.com/dmca/' }
];

const lastUpdated = '2025-01-01';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonicalUrl="https://fixmissingdll.com/dmca/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(generateBreadcrumbSchema(breadcrumbs))} />
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="text-sm mb-6">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
        <li><a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Home</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li class="text-gray-600">DMCA Policy</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">DMCA Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        FixMissingDLL.com respects the intellectual property rights of others and expects 
        users of our website to do the same. In accordance with the Digital Millennium 
        Copyright Act of 1998 ("DMCA"), we will respond expeditiously to claims of copyright 
        infringement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Position on DLL Files</h2>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <p class="text-blue-800 mb-4">
          DLL files provided on this website are offered for educational and troubleshooting 
          purposes. Many DLL files are components of software packages that are freely 
          distributable (such as Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable, DirectX, etc.).
        </p>
        <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
          We always recommend downloading official runtime packages from Microsoft or the 
          original software vendor as the primary solution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Filing a DMCA Takedown Notice</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        If you believe that content available on our website infringes your copyright, you 
        may submit a DMCA takedown notice. To be effective, the notice must be in writing 
        and include the following information:
      </p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>
          <strong>Physical or electronic signature</strong> of a person authorized to act 
          on behalf of the copyright owner
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Identification of the copyrighted work</strong> claimed to have been 
          infringed (or a representative list if multiple works)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Identification of the infringing material</strong> and information 
          reasonably sufficient to locate it on our website (please provide specific URLs)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Your contact information</strong> including address, telephone number, 
          and email address
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>A statement</strong> that you have a good faith belief that use of the 
          material is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>A statement</strong> that the information in the notification is accurate, 
          and under penalty of perjury, that you are authorized to act on behalf of the 
          copyright owner
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Where to Send DMCA Notices</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>DMCA Agent:</strong></p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
          Email: <a href="mailto:dmca@fixmissingdll.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">dmca@fixmissingdll.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 mb-0">
          Subject Line: DMCA Takedown Notice
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Counter-Notification</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        If you believe your content was removed by mistake or misidentification, you may 
        file a counter-notification. The counter-notification must include:
      </p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>Your physical or electronic signature</li>
        <li>Identification of the material that was removed and its previous location</li>
        <li>A statement under penalty of perjury that you have a good faith belief that 
            the material was removed as a result of mistake or misidentification</li>
        <li>Your name, address, telephone number, and email address</li>
        <li>A statement that you consent to the jurisdiction of the federal court in your 
            district and that you will accept service of process from the person who 
            provided the original DMCA notice</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Repeat Infringers</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        In accordance with the DMCA, we will terminate, in appropriate circumstances, users 
        or account holders who are deemed to be repeat infringers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Response Time</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We aim to respond to valid DMCA notices within 48-72 hours. Upon receiving a valid 
        notice, we will:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Remove or disable access to the allegedly infringing material</li>
        <li>Notify the content provider (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Provide information about counter-notification procedures</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">⚠️ False Claims Warning</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700 mb-0">
          Please note that under Section 512(f) of the DMCA, any person who knowingly 
          materially misrepresents that material is infringing may be subject to liability 
          for damages, including costs and attorneys' fees incurred by us or our users.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
